body:
@MicaelCarvalho  I understand your point; but it actually works. The code below successfully prints the operations from my loaded graph outside of the "with" block. 
```
with tf.Graph().as_default() as graph:
     tf.import_graph(...)

for op in graph.get_operations():
     print(op)

return graph
```
